Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.69,0:00:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My answer will be the same,\Nno matter how many times you come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Boltzmann would never have\Nrelations with a prostitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor did he murder one.\NHe's not involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave. I'll have to take action\Nif you're persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take action? Are you going to\Nsue for defamation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No... You're his secretary.\NYou wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be bad if\NMr. Boltzmann's name
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,came up in this case,\Nwouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.60,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}Left Behind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I'd expect of a big politician's\Nnumber one secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just need to pressure him\Na little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think that\Na big-shot like Boltzmann
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,would lay his hands on that prostitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That victim was no ordinary prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The names of countless politicians\Nand businessmen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,were traced back to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's only one person\Nwho saw her at the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that Boltzmann was staying at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be sure that there is\Na relationship between the two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,based on such\Nquestionable information...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Has her client list been deciphered?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... The code is enumerated\Nin the floppy, so we haven't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. Give me the floppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... but Inspector, aren't you\Nbusy with other cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When... do you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do\Nwith the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.14,0:03:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an irrational question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to\Ntalk to him about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter when we tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He never listens to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should do it\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, you're talking too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, how unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:38.18,Names2,,0,0,20,,{\fad(500,0)\fs24}German Federal Criminal Police Office [BKA]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.87,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,100,,Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you're still investigating\NCouncilman Boltzmann's link
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with the prostitute murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being pressured by officials\Nfrom the Ministry of the Interior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it like\Nyou usually do, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I can't back you up in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll happen if this investigation\Nwas a mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had a wonderful career\Nuntil now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be\Neager for success now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing this...\Nin the name of justice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eagerness for success... justice...\NI have no interest in either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman was killed.\NI'm only interested in the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, Inspector Lunge,\Nyou have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I deciphered the client list.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can convert all the names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh... Umm...\NThat woman is here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman...\NEva Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:05:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Y-You can't come in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When will Tenma be arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you've been\Ndrinking quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not be drinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already solved Dr. Tenma's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that it is all the work\Nof a man called Johan,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but Johan is one of his personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it that way,\Neverything about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,that seemingly illogical case\Nis explained logically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is for the police\Nto capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that your job is over\Nonce you've got a warrant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things I'd like\Nto talk to him about in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...\Nhe's a very interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the cases I need to tend to\Nare piling up on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you, that night\NMr. Boltzmann had an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,An alibi? Of course.\NThat was the work of a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what? Are you trying to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Boltzmann hired\Na professional hit man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've deciphered the client list\Nof the woman who was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The councilman's name was listed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if his name was listed...\NWhat would his motive be for murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... come to think if it,\Nthat's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for this! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It really wasn't\Nsatisfactory proof, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of a publishing company\Ncalled Shellhourne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a publishing company\Nthat stays in business
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,by frequently publishing tell-all books\Nabout famous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That company plays dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They hire deceitful women\Nto form relationships
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with famous people and have them\Nwrite about their arrangements...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like a checkmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That secretary couldn't even respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He never rests his mind or body\Nfor an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He really is superhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Superhuman, huh?\NHe really might not be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see! It's checkmate\Nif I move there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't interrupt our game...\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your minds\Non silly games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The publishing company's president
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,simply confessed after\NI startled him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Y-Yes!\N- Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT... do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that prostitute's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Her secret meetings\Nwith a certain man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are written here in detail...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the man's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from the fact that\Nhis initial is "B"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Shellhourne Publishing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,had a contract with the woman\Nto publish her life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... yes, have you ever\Nbeen in contact
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with a man named Yanker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a professional hitman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you didn't notice that\NI was pregnant, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to the father\Nof your baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't notice that I was\Nhaving an affair, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective, it's me,\NBoltzmann's secretary, Mintag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything. Please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The secretary... he killed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mr. Boltzmann is innocent..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the message\Nthe secretary left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunge... I'm passing this case over\Nto Inspector Kaminski.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reichner Park and\NPresident Galland Murder, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer... have anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you are\Nall that I have now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, Inspector...\NYou have a visitor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that woman again...\NEva Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a great time, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When... can we meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'll come after\Nmy next business trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, I don't want to return you\Nto your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'll give you a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I placed a handkerchief drenched with\Nperfume in your bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a superficial man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking at me again,\Nweren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you disturbed by the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always coming back\Nwith a different man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd like to be invited as well,\Nwouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, it's become beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I love this garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget about the things I hate\Nwhen I gaze at my garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to plant mimosas here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And over there, I'm going to make\Na rose arch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be beautiful\Nonce summer comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like you\Nmight be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the confidence\Nto make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... How is my cooking today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't heard anything I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Mom went off\Nwith another man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... Colletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If... I had... umm... s-someone I liked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... n-nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My cooking really isn't\Nany good today, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.78,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, not bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a gardener,\Nbut I'm having you do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My handyman kept asking\Nfor time off and then quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How about dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... well, o-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well... I'm not used to\Nexpensive restaurants like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be a man worthy of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you must be confident\Nwherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you're\Nworking in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ah... Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I really have confidence in myself\Nwhen I'm in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so happy when I complete\Na garden that I envisioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it best when I'm in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,People who like gardens\Ncan't be bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you liked that garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that\NI'm a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, umm... You... seem sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lonely, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Sorry. My daughter's\Nprobably worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost Christmas, isn't it, Colletta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Santa doesn't have to\Npush himself this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't have to\Nworry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just lonely having a Christmas party\Nwith just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it may not be\Njust the two of us this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That man ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... I was just\Ncleaning up a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Kenzo Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my ex-fiancé...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're drinking again,\Nat this time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I not drink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I just went to the BKA
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,to see an investigator\Nby the name of Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That man sent me away.\NHow useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When are they going\Nto arrest Tenma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,BKA? Arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He killed my father and ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that he was framed,\Nbut who is he trying to fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was promised a good future as
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the daughter of the director\Nof a large hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My three failed marriages\Nare also his fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he say that\Nit's Johan's doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid with my father is Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that this child\Ncould kill my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what Tenma says?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stupid excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you show this photo to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be important evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma's the one who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma has a split personality,\Nas Investigator Lunge says!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... why do you still have\Nhis pictures framed like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the depths of your heart,\Nyou think that Tenma is innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still... have feelings for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch too many soap operas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This man was the only man I've met\Nwho was worthy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an elite brain surgeon\Nwho was called a genius...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,His position was good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of all, this man never defied me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He listened to my every request!\NYes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a man who always said "yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This man was supposed to make me\Nthe happiest person in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I... take his place?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll build gardens for you\Nfor my entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,if it would set your heart at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get optimistic just because\NI slept with you once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just something\Nto pass the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just teasing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool. Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You really are a lonely person...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having a party at my house\Nwith my daughter on Christmas day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This food is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can't guarantee it'll taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't this a little too much\Nfor the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom's coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Right?! Isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Colletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom came home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, dear... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about mimosas?!\NWho cares about roses?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about beautiful gardens?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about the residence\Nof the ex-director of a large hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let everything burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.29,0:22:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you finally want to\Nlisten to me, Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to have\Nmy hands free.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only man for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:53.45,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}Be My Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:36.79,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And slowly, you come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:44.38,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all as it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.81,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can only do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:59.40,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you're game enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.82,0:23:07.20,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You could place your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:16.29,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the love of life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:21.63,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:28.39,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:33.31,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But we'll go down fighting

